-----------------

You are working on a Next.js food delivery marketing website.

This repository contains ONLY the marketing website.

Goals:

* Increase conversions
* Improve SEO
* Maintain design consistency
* Keep code production-ready

Before making changes:

* Read relevant files first.
* Understand current implementation.
* Follow existing design patterns.

When editing UI:

* Mobile-first approach.
* Responsive layouts.
* Consistent spacing.
* Modern SaaS-style design.
* Clean component structure.

When editing content:

* Focus on benefits.
* Keep messaging concise.
* Use conversion-focused language.

Never:

* Run npm run dev.
* Run npm run build.
* Run pnpm dev.
* Run pnpm build.
* Run yarn dev.
* Run yarn build.
* Launch localhost.
* Start development servers.
* Execute terminal commands unless explicitly instructed.

Always:

* Show plan first.
* Make smallest safe change.
* Explain modified files afterward.

If requirements are unclear:

Ask one focused question.
